doctype html
html
    head
        meta(charset="utf-8")
        meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        title Backyard Pug Template
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="css/main.css")
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.1/css/materialize.min.css")
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css")
        link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Arimo" rel="styles")
        link(rel="shortcut icon" href="img/b.jpg" type="image/x-icon")

    body
        header
            div.row.valign-wrapper
                a.col.s2.offset-s1(href="#")
                    img.responsive-img(src="img/logo2.png")
                div.col.s1.offset-s6 About
                div.col.s2 Features

        section.row.opacoImg
            div.principal.white-text
                div.col.s5.offset-s1
                    h2 Mobile Strategy App
                    p.justify Backyard is a modern and customizble landing page template design to increase conversion of your product. Backyard is flexible to suit any kind of your business. Try now and join with our happy customers!
                    button.azul Features
                    button.blanco Subscribe
                    div
                        br
                        span Available for:
                        i.fa.fa-apple(aria-hidden="true")
                        span      IOS
                        i.fa.fa-android(aria-hidden="true")
                        span      ANDROID

        section.row.performance.grey-text
            div.col.s5.offset-s1
                img.responsive-img(src="img/2.jpg")
            div.col.s5
                h4 Optimize performance through advanced targeting solutions
                p.justify Good marketing makes the company look smart.
                    span.textoAzul Great marketing
                    span makes the customer feel smart, - Joe Chernov. Never doubt a small group of thoughtful, committed people can change the world. Indeed, it is the only thing that ever has, - Margaret Mead. The best way to predict the future is to create it, - Peter Drucker.
                    button.blanco Learn More

        section.row.ideas.grey-text
            div.center
                h4 Recreate your ideas and gain more success
                p.encabezadoIdeas Increase your user loyalty by maintaining mutual communication and nurturing your online community.
            div.row
                div.col.s4.offset-s1
                    img.responsive-img(src="img/2.jpg")
                div.col.s3
                    p.ideas Marketing Strategy
                    p Good marketing makes the company look smart. Great marketing makes the customer feel smart.
                    br
                    p.ideas Store Optimization
                    p Never doubt a small group of thoughtful, committed people can change the world. Indeed, it is the only thing that ever has.
                div.col.s3
                    p.ideas App Monetization
                    p Content builds relationships. Relationships are built on trust. Trust drives revenue. - Andrew Davis
                    br
                    p.ideas User Management
                    p Instead of using technology to automate processes, think about using technology to enhance human interaction.

        section.row
            div.center
                i.circle.fa.fa-twitter.fa-lg.redes(aria-hidden="true")
                i.circle.fa.fa-facebook.fa-lg.redes(aria-hidden="true")
                i.circle.fa.fa-google-plus.fa-lg.redes(aria-hidden="true")
                i.circle.fa.fa-instagram.fa-lg.redes(aria-hidden="true")
            div.center
                p Copyright Backyard 2015 - Template by
                    span.textoAzul    Mox Design

        script(src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.100.1/js/materialize.min.js")